    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_3494438093457995186.png",
                "id": "talent96085",
                "key": "線列槍刺·改",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "線列槍刺·改"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此技能結算後：</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.899903 -0.00123695 -0.00312543)\">如果我方手牌中含有</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">超量裝藥彈頭</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.899903 -0.00123695 -0.00312543)\">，則</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.899903 -0.00123695 -0.00312543)\">1張並治療我方受傷最多的角色1點。</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/52cd1e5b70e7ea798b5a41cd9a51fbef_5800484259799457150.png",
                "id": "talent79238",
                "key": "近迫式急促攔射",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "近迫式急促攔射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，在敵方場上生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">二重毀傷彈</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">二重毀傷彈</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所在陣營切換角色後：</span>對切換到的角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/a36c7a9c9512124baf0b482d8dc69912_3729963044076148809.png",
                "id": "talent76004",
                "key": "圓陣擲彈爆轟術",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "圓陣擲彈爆轟術"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">敵方角色受到超載反應傷害後：</span>生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">超量裝藥彈頭（</span>每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/4b48c030ba601eab2fe4d2375057a617_6151011494096034807.png",
                "id": "talent75726",
                "key": "縱陣武力統籌",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "縱陣武力統籌"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">戰鬥行動：</span>對敵方「出戰角色」造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此牌被捨棄時：</span>對敵方「出戰角色」造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2726039240498422525.png",
                "id": "talent94989",
                "key": "超量裝藥彈頭",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/5dca55a012526872199ffb25f0129241_4455298171776218753.png",
                "title": "超量裝藥彈頭"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5287058139495960922.png",
                "id": "talent12291",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2999571164676152053.png",
                "id": "talent10809",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_2194847893348258819.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">戰鬥行動</span></p><p>我方執行了一次戰鬥行動後，會輪到對方行動。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">打出具有此規則的手牌是一個戰鬥行動，而非快速行動。</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span></p><p>透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6971972697886981017.png",
